responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "AD85603C439BC1562DED87B8B1F1013B", "This is amazing information! We\'ve still so much to learn about how Verra has changed since our peoples left it behind. You say that the Ashen Flame tribe claim custody of our Riverlands? No doubt the Expeditionary Forces will have something to say about that! Still, what I wouldn\'t give to put my hands on some of those stone carvings you saw. Perhaps in time the Academy will send me into the bush on my own expeditions. Until the next time.")
name: DD_CSQ_0071_Monroe_37
